{"tid":548083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經] 住喺香港廿幾年嘅迷思-究竟樓上鑽乜撚嘢？","createTime":"2018-02-02T07:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T01:55:10.000Z","uid":6842,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d479255b928d50f32efe75e7aa41cce680d647a1","tid":548083,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T07:01:08.000Z","msg":"屋企人好耐之前講過我都唔信，呢一兩年真係火都嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母今日放假 諗住好地地喺屋企瞓覺 你老味十二點幾開始鑽 轟轟轟轟鑽到依家都仲嘈緊 有冇人知樓上平時喺屋企做緊咩？日常娛樂係咪就係鑽牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我逢親留喺屋企十居八九樓上都係鑽呀鑿呀拉枱拉凳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母 上去同佢反映又講 哦唔好意思會小心啲 屌你 完撚全冇改善到 日又嘈夜又嘈 真係好撚煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 純粹打上嚟呻下 應該都冇得搞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(同食蕉講過，佢哋hea9我) <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我決定以後嘈一次就上嚟推一次，記錄低佢哋可以有幾撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b289e586bd82afa4b6dde1ccdff9a5bef0fb77c4","tid":548083,"uid":166675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T07:05:16.000Z","msg":"裝返隻低音炮貼撚住個天花板<br />\n記得買隔音綿包撚住佢, 最好整個箱仔比支炮用, 唔係嘈撚埋自己<br />\n之後你中意樓上聽咩歌聽咩大悲咒隨你喜歡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77229667b46d483eb210318774949108ad9d7d8","tid":548083,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T07:05:29.000Z","msg":"好多人都有的問題<br />\n自己個單位 附近總係有一間野 係長期用電鑽<br />\n長唔係一兩日 甚至1，2個月<br />\n<br />\n是以年計 得閒就鑽一陣"},{"pid":"b716773e3152aba2abd92afc634eaff5bd06e6a9","tid":548083,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b289e586bd82afa4b6dde1ccdff9a5bef0fb77c4","tid":548083,"uid":166675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T07:05:16.000Z","msg":"裝返隻低音炮貼撚住個天花板<br />\n記得買隔音綿包撚住佢, 最好整個箱仔比支炮用, 唔係嘈撚埋自己<br />\n之後你中意樓上聽咩歌聽咩大悲咒隨你喜歡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T07:06:55.000Z","msg":"有得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢做初一我做十五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86afbb6d3f31118c0f000b7b6ce2e321cc3b7e8e","tid":548083,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"拉枱拉凳聲<br />\n有好大機會係冷縮熱漲D鋼根既聲黎"},{"pid":"44fa3788595368482af082298bde63008f02dda6","tid":548083,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f77229667b46d483eb210318774949108ad9d7d8","tid":548083,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T07:05:29.000Z","msg":"好多人都有的問題<br />\n自己個單位 附近總係有一間野 係長期用電鑽<br />\n長唔係一兩日 甚至1，2個月<br />\n<br />\n是以年計 得閒就鑽一陣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T07:08:53.000Z","msg":"我知 出面都好多呢啲po 但究竟係咩真係咁多人鍾意用電鑽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我又唔係好覺，至少我識嘅人冇人會咁搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93fb50d2a49c69c8baa341f4d46e099bfbd47c6","tid":548083,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T07:09:30.000Z","msg":"你每朝拎個啞鈴撞上去幾下佢好快收皮"},{"pid":"d10382c9cc69276a9c120db6904549983ec46cc1","tid":548083,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86afbb6d3f